a_i, b_i \in {0,1}
a_i=b_i
\sum_{i=0}^\infty a_i(-2)^i = \sum_{i=0}^\infty b_i(-2)^i
N
0 = \sum_{i=0}^N (a_i-b_i)(-2)^i = (a_N-b_N)(-2)^N+\sum_{i=0}^{N-1} (a_i-b_i)(-2)^i.
(a_N-b_N)(-2)^N
2^N
-2^N
0 = -2^N + \sum_{i=0}^{N-1} (a_i-b_i)(-2)^i \leq -2^N + \sum_{i=0}^{N-1} |a_i-b_i|2^i < -2^N + 2^N -1 = -1,
